      "content": "hey, so for this roleplay... i'm playing this character who just found out their entire existence is being patched out of the server. like, they aren't just dying, they're being deleted from history. everything they ever did or felt is just gonna be zeroed out. i'm struggling with how to play them... it just feels like there's no point in even trying to fight it if nothing's left behind. it's all just so empty.",
